Trinity:

She jumped as the top of the pod opened up. "Who...who are you?" She 
took a small step back from his hand. She wasn't sure if this bot was 
someone nice, or one of those bots that her mother used to tell her 
stories about. Like the space pirates that killed and plundered. Or 
maybe he was one of those bots who served the Predacon empire and 
tortured bots for fun.  Or maybe he was just some sick bot that ate 
kittens.  
She looked up at him with a 'I'm not sure about you,' kind of look on 
her face. "What's going on around here? Where would you take me 
mister...ah..mister.  Say, what's your name anyway?"
